Hello,

I'm thinking about  purchasing a Dell 2408WFP but it  is not possible to
set accurately  the sharpness setting  (e.g.  it can  only be set  by 25
increments). As  I'm using GNU/Linux (my  graphic card is  a Radeon X300
and I would like to plug in the monitor via VGA).

I'm wondering  whether it may be  possible to adjust  this setting using
ddccontrol. Some people  were able to set this  setting with SoftMCCS as
reported there[0],  but do you think it  may be possible to  do the same
with  ddccontrol? (It  is the  first  time I  need to  set such  setting
without OSD,  so I don't  know almost anything  about DDC except  what I
read on the ddccontrol documentation...)

Cheers,
Arnaud Fontaine

[0] http://64.233.183.132/search?q=cache:caIZ8UNfU8cJ:www.dellcommunity.com/supportforums/board/message%3Fboard.id%3Ddim_monitor%26message.id%3D92338+ddccontrol+Dell+2408WFP&hl=en&ct=clnk&cd=4


